h3. Summary
Back when using Classic Boards, users are able to specify a *Start date*, *Release date* and *End date*. However, since Classic Boards are deprecated, this no longer exists. With the *End date*, there should also be a dashboard gadget which displays the number of days left until the End date.

This would be useful for users who do *not* fully use Agile methodology. Just a simple dashboard showing the number of days to the *End date* is sufficient.

