Custom Fields have a context: For what issue types and for what projects do they apply?

As a JIRA installation grows, hundreds of custom issue types are not unthinkable. As a JIRA SysAdmin, one is presented with a gigantic list of issue types that likely do not apply in the context the SysAdmin is currently working.

It would be nice if we could filter the view of such custom fields, at least by project and by applicable issue type. Other filtering options could be considered. That way it would clean up the view, especially valuable in large installations.

