{quote}
The process for automatic renewal is flawed and confusing to the customer. You need to be much more explicit about the automatic renewal being only the automatic taking of the renewal fee, and that a manual process to update the licence keys is still required. Better still, the products could provide some centralised control of applying the licence keys so that this can be done from one place, via one login. Even better still would be to provide a method of validating the licences which does not require copy and paste or button pressing.
{quote}
